#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:123
msgid "Added a fully offline Noble Qur'an module featuring the Qur'anic text in Uthmanic orthography (rasm), translations, mushaf-style navigation, diacritic-aware search, saved reading positions, and adjustable typography."
msgstr ""
"Ditambahkan modul Al-Qur'an Karim yang sepenuhnya dapat digunakan secara offline, yang menampilkan teks Al-Qur'an dalam ejaan Utsmaniyah (rasm), terjemahan, navigasi bergaya mushaf, fitur pencarian yang mendukung tanda baca, penyimpanan posisi bacaan, serta "
"tipografi yang dapat disesuaikan."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:124
msgid "Added Mawaqit API integration as an alternative prayer times source."
msgstr "Ditambahkan integrasi API Mawaqit sebagai sumber waktu shalat alternatif."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:125
msgid "Added ICU-backed localization for location and timezone labels, plus validated custom IANA timezone editing."
msgstr "Ditambahkan lokalisasi yang didukung ICU untuk label lokasi dan zona waktu, serta pengeditan zona waktu IANA khusus yang telah diverifikasi."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:126
msgid "Reorganized settings into clearer General, Prayer Setup, and Alerts sections with improved inline editing behavior."
msgstr "Pengaturan telah diorganisir ulang menjadi bagian-bagian yang lebih jelas, yaitu Umum, Pengaturan Shalat, dan Pemberitahuan, dengan peningkatan pada fitur pengeditan langsung."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:127
msgid "Fixed Snap tray icon visibility via an upstream patch to ksni (resolves AppArmor D-Bus blocking)."
msgstr "Perbaikan masalah visibilitas ikon baki Snap melalui tambalan hulu pada ksni (mengatasi masalah pemblokiran D-Bus oleh AppArmor)."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:134
msgid "Fixed Snap autostart and notification icon rendering."
msgstr "Masalah terkait pengaktifan otomatis Snap dan tampilan ikon notifikasi telah diperbaiki."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:135
msgid "Improved locale detection and fallback logic."
msgstr "Peningkatan dalam deteksi wilayah dan logika cadangan."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:142
msgid "Fixed Flatpak autostart failure and missing --background flag."
msgstr "Perbaikan masalah kegagalan autostart Flatpak dan hilangnya opsi --background."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:143
msgid "Fixed over-translation of proper nouns (e.g., Muslim) in non-English locales."
msgstr "Masalah terjemahan berlebihan pada nama-nama khusus (misalnya, Muslim) di wilayah non-Inggris telah diperbaiki."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:144
msgid "Added new localized AppStream screenshots for improved store presence."
msgstr "Telah ditambahkan tangkapan layar AppStream yang telah dilokalkan untuk meningkatkan daya tarik di toko aplikasi."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:151
msgid "Fixed tray icon translation extraction (Quit and Open Khushu entries)."
msgstr "Perbaikan pengambilan terjemahan ikon baki (entri Keluar dan Buka Khushu)."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:152
msgid "Fixed AppStream metadata translation (descriptions and keywords)."
msgstr "Fixed AppStream metadata translation (descriptions and keywords)."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:153
msgid "Improved tray behavior to update labels immediately on language change."
msgstr "Improved tray behavior to update labels immediately on language change."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:160
msgid "Initial stable release of Khushu."
msgstr "Initial stable release of Khushu."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:88
msgid "Fixed data loss on exit with synchronous atomic config save."
msgstr "Fixed data loss on exit with synchronous atomic config save."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:89
msgid "Fixed autostart portal command double-wrapping."
msgstr "Masalah pembungkus ganda pada perintah autostart portal telah diperbaiki."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:90
msgid "Fixed notification toggles reverting on restart due to UI override."
msgstr "Masalah tombol pengaturan notifikasi yang kembali ke pengaturan awal saat perangkat dihidupkan ulang akibat penggantian antarmuka pengguna telah diperbaiki."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:91
msgid "Fixed audio selection reverting on restart due to file check on bundled presets."
msgstr "Fixed audio selection reverting on restart due to file check on bundled presets."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:98
msgid "Improved audio playback engine with streaming decode."
msgstr "Improved audio playback engine with streaming decode."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:99
msgid "Improved Qibla compass performance with Pango and bearing caching."
msgstr "Peningkatan kinerja kompas kiblat berkat Pango dan penyimpanan data arah."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:100
msgid "Improved timer controller with daily state caching."
msgstr "Pengendali timer yang disempurnakan dengan penyimpanan sementara status harian."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:101
msgid "Improved config persistence with singleton save channel."
msgstr "Improved config persistence with singleton save channel."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:102
msgid "Fixed application crashes caused by notification re-entrancy."
msgstr "Fixed application crashes caused by notification re-entrancy."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:103
msgid "Fixed configuration data race when saving from multiple threads."
msgstr "Fixed configuration data race when saving from multiple threads."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:104
msgid "Fixed thread safety issues in locale setup and audio initialization."
msgstr "Fixed thread safety issues in locale setup and audio initialization."

#: data/appdata/io.github.sniper1720.khushu.metainfo.xml.in:105
msgid "Replaced 26 unsafe unwrap() calls with proper error messages."
msgstr "Mengganti 26 panggilan fungsi `unwrap()` yang tidak aman dengan pesan kesalahan yang tepat."

